          </li>
          <li>National Training Officer, NIMSA Mental Advocacy Campaign (2022-2023)</li>
          <li>Chief Editor, Nile University Medical Students' Association Magazine (2022-2023)</li>
          <li>President, The Nile Student Network (2022-2023)</li>
